c: 3
v: 199
t: "Toto mubandu bahebwa eshitabu balimwo basuubilanga Nyasaye nende kalia keshibwa khwinywe nende kalia kabeshilibwa, behotselesilinjia Nyasaye. Shibakusinjia tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye khubukusi obufwoola tawe. Bali nende omurungo kwabu khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi.Toto Nyasaye ni Omwangu wakhubala"